\(E\)])\) + \*SuperscriptBox[SubscriptBox[\(v\), \(0, \*SubscriptBox[\(e\), \
\(D\)]\)], \(2\)]\)], SqrtBox[\(\*SuperscriptBox[SubscriptBox[\(v\), \(esc\\\ \
